cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CR 

The paper deals with the problem of detecting unusual events or anomalies in video data, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The specific application domain is autonomous driving, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the issue of robustness in machine learning systems, which is also relevant to computer security (cs.CR).
